Hello everyone,

Have you ever wondered what it takes to land an exchange or international
intern?
If yes, then this is the session for you!



INTERNATIONAL OPPORTUNITIES FUNDAE SESSIONFOR UNDERGRADS
Date : Friday, 26th August
Venue: ICSR Auditorium
Time : 7:00 pm 

Questions to be addressed for Exchange program

    Why an exchange programme?  Pros and Cons.
    Opportunities available  Universities & scholarship/funding
    What is the correct time/semester to go for an exchange?
    What is the procedure for applying? & what all matter?  SOP, Resume
   etc.
    Post selection process.

International Research Intern Opportunities:

    International research interns other then popular programs like MITACS
   and DAAD
    Program specific fundae session by previous intern fellows
    Funding and application procedure

Not to mention, trade secrets such as the fact that exchange grades
won't appear on your grade card will be given. So don't miss the session!

